| `certification_status` | VARCHAR(20) | ✅ | 认证状态: none/pending/approved/rejected |
| `certification_time` | DATETIME | ❌ | 认证时间 |
| `certification_expire_time` | DATETIME | ❌ | 认证过期时间 |
| **小程序备案状态** |
